---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — AmbitiousOS"
  description="Privacy policy for AmbitiousOS and the Reading Ambitiously newsletter."
>
  <main class="section-padding">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-custom">
      <nav class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-text-secondary">Privacy</span>
      </nav>

      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        AmbitiousOS (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;our,&rdquo; &ldquo;us&rdquo;) is operated by Reading Ambitiously.
        We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.
        This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Account Information</h3>
      <p>When you request access or sign in, we collect your email address and name. Authentication is handled via Supabase.</p>

      <h3>Usage Data</h3>
      <p>
        We use <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong>, a privacy-first analytics tool that does not use cookies,
        does not collect personal data, and is fully GDPR/CCPA compliant. We collect aggregate page views,
        referrer sources, and device types — never individual tracking data.
      </p>

      <h3>Conversations</h3>
      <p>If you use the AI chat feature in AmbitiousOS, your conversation history is stored to provide continuity. Conversations are private to your account.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To provide and improve AmbitiousOS</li>
        <li>To send you the Reading Ambitiously newsletter (if subscribed)</li>
        <li>To communicate about your account and access</li>
        <li>To understand aggregate usage patterns (via Plausible)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. We use the following service providers:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — authentication and database</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — website hosting</li>
        <li><strong>Fly.io</strong> — API hosting</li>
        <li><strong>Resend</strong> — transactional email</li>
        <li><strong>Plausible</strong> — privacy-first analytics</li>
        <li><strong>Substack</strong> — newsletter distribution</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This marketing site (<strong>ambitiousos.com</strong>) does not use cookies.
        The AmbitiousOS app (os.readingambitiously.com) uses essential authentication cookies only — no tracking cookies.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe from the newsletter at any time</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:jack@readingambitiously.com">jack@readingambitiously.com</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .prose-custom h1 { @apply text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6; }
  .prose-custom h2 { @apply text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mt-10 mb-3; }
  .prose-custom h3 { @apply text-lg font-medium text-text-primary mt-6 mb-2; }
  .prose-custom p { @apply text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4; }
  .prose-custom ul { @apply text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4 pl-6 list-disc space-y-1; }
  .prose-custom a { @apply text-galaxy-sage hover:underline; }
  .prose-custom strong { @apply text-text-primary; }
</style>
